<plot>A subtle mix of horror, thriller and drama, THE DIRT, centers on a married woman, a photographer, and her all-consuming wish to have a child. During the course of the film, this woman develops a very morbid relationship with an unusual plant that grows in her living room, one that holds many secrets-but none as dark as the woman has herself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?553511</url></doc>
